Image optimized size for wesite

header image - 1024px => 1024*768px upto 200KB

bg image -> 1920*1080 => 16:9, atleast 72ppi

logo -> 250*100px, upto => 320px*70-100px
if retina option dim double

Global rule : 
 jpg for everything
png & svg for logo & illustrations
for wordpress -> plugin svg support

Image compression tools:
optimazilla
tinyJPG
